Package io.helidon.config.spi

Interface ConfigNode.ListNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<ConfigNode>, ConfigNode, Iterable<ConfigNode>, List<ConfigNode>, Supplier<String>
    Enclosing interface:
    ConfigNode
    public static interface ConfigNode.ListNode
extends ConfigNode, List<ConfigNode>
    ConfigNode-based list of configuration values.

    List contains instance of ConfigNode.ValueNode, ConfigNode.ListNode as well as ConfigNode.ObjectNode.

    NOTE: Do not implement this interface yourself but rather use builder().
